trans-unit.source: A deep copy of a <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildPropertyGroup> creates a new XML element to reference so that both copies of the <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildPropertyGroup> can be independently modified.
trans-unit.target: En dyp kopi av en <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildPropertyGroup>oppretter en ny XML-elementet å referere til slik at både overfører av den <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildPropertyGroup>kan endres uavhengig.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildPropertyGroup> </xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildPropertyGroup>
